<h3 id="features">Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Pinned Posts</li>
  <li>Configurable theme mode</li>
  <li>Double-level Categories</li>
  <li>Last modified date for posts</li>
  <li>Table of Contents</li>
  <li>Automatically recommend related posts</li>
  <li>Syntax highlighting</li>
  <li>Mathematical expressions</li>
  <li>Mermaid diagram &amp; flowchart</li>
  <li>Search</li>
  <li>Atom Feeds</li>
  <li>Disqus Comments</li>
  <li>Google Analytics</li>
  <li>GA Pageviews reporting (Advanced)</li>
  <li>SEO and Performance Optimization</li>
</ul>

